<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>{{title}}</title>
        <script
            src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/4e0194f4de.js"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/navbar-styles.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/universal-styles.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/page-styles.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        {{! Application header - imported from appNavbar partial}}

        <div>
            {{> appNavbar}}
        </div>

        <div class="main-body">
            <h2 class="main-body__headerWelcome">Welcome to <span>Jawaab Paao </span></h2>
            <div class="main-body__content">
                <p>Hello, We would like to WELCOME you to Jawaab Paao. </p>
                <p>We have
                    built this platform as tool for Knowledge sharing among
                    users. Using this platform users can post their questions
                    regarding any topic they don't know the answers and request
                    for the same as well.
                </p>
                <p>Users can also write answers for the questions already asked
                    by other users.
                </p>
                <p>Also they can post a Question with its Answer for sharing the
                    knowledge they have on any topic with other users.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="main-body__buttonWrapper">
                <div class="main-body__button">
                    <form action="/articles" method="GET">
                        <button type="submit">Get Started</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
    </body>
</html>